{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/airbnb-javascript-style-guide","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7c716630-85ca-55cb-8502-08224aedee5a","html":"<p>Đây là một loạt bài viết nói về phong cách viết javascript của Airbnb mà mình dịch từ <a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/javascript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">github</a>. Trong quá trình dịch không tránh khỏi sai sót, cũng như một số thuật ngữ mình không thể dịch thì mình sẽ để nguyên văn.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kiểu-dữ-liệu\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ki%E1%BB%83u-d%E1%BB%AF-li%E1%BB%87u\" aria-label=\"kiểu dữ liệu permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Kiểu dữ liệu</h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-kiểu-dữ-liệu-primitives-nguyên-thủy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-ki%E1%BB%83u-d%E1%BB%AF-li%E1%BB%87u-primitives-nguy%C3%AAn-th%E1%BB%A7y\" aria-label=\"11 kiểu dữ liệu primitives nguyên thủy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.1 Kiểu dữ liệu primitives( nguyên thủy)</h3>\n<p>Các kiểu dữ liệu primitives trong javascript:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>string</li>\n<li>number</li>\n<li>boolean</li>\n<li>null</li>\n<li>undefined</li>\n<li>symbol</li>\n<li>bigint</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> bar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// => 1, 9</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Symbols và BigInts , vì vậy chúng ta không nên sử dụng trên môi trường trình duyệt bởi vì nó không hỗ trợ native.</p>\n<h3 id=\"kiểu-dữ-liệu-complex\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ki%E1%BB%83u-d%E1%BB%AF-li%E1%BB%87u-complex\" aria-label=\"kiểu dữ liệu complex permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Kiểu dữ liệu complex</h3>\n<p>Các kiểu dữ liệu nguyên primitives trong javascript:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>object</li>\n<li>array</li>\n<li>function</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> bar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbar<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// => 9, 9</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"references-tham-chiếu\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references-tham-chi%E1%BA%BFu\" aria-label=\"references tham chiếu permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>References( Tham chiếu)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-sử-dụng-const-cho-references-tránh-sử-dụng-var\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-s%E1%BB%AD-d%E1%BB%A5ng-const-cho-references-tr%C3%A1nh-s%E1%BB%AD-d%E1%BB%A5ng-var\" aria-label=\"21 sử dụng const cho references tránh sử dụng var permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1 Sử dụng const cho references, tránh sử dụng var</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tại sao? Vì sử dụng const bạn không thể thay đổi references, nó có thể dẫn đến bugs hoặc khó hiểu code.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// bad</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// good</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"22-nếu-phải-thay-đổi-giá-trị-sử-dụng-let-thay-thế-var\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#22-n%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BA%A3i-thay-%C4%91%E1%BB%95i-gi%C3%A1-tr%E1%BB%8B-s%E1%BB%AD-d%E1%BB%A5ng-let-thay-th%E1%BA%BF-var\" aria-label=\"22 nếu phải thay đổi giá trị sử dụng let thay thế var permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.2 Nếu phải thay đổi giá trị, sử dụng let thay thế var</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tại sao? vì <code class=\"language-text\">let</code> là block-scoped( vòng đời trong block), còn <code class=\"language-text\">var</code> function-scoped( vòng đời function)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// bad</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// good</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"23-const-và-let-đều-là-block-scoped\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#23-const-v%C3%A0-let-%C4%91%E1%BB%81u-l%C3%A0-block-scoped\" aria-label=\"23 const và let đều là block scoped permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.3 const và let đều là block-scoped</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// const và let chỉ tồn tại trong blocks khai báo chúng</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Uncaught ReferenceError: a is not defined</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Uncaught ReferenceError: b is not defined</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"/posts/airbnb-javascript-style-guide-2\">Xem tiếp phần 2</a></p>\n<p>Cảm ơn các bạn đã theo dõi!</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/airbnb-javascript-style-guide","tagSlugs":["/tag/javascript/","/tag/clean-code/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-04-04","description":"Đây là một loạt bài viết nói về phong cách viết javascript của Airbnb mà mình dịch từ github.","tags":["javascript","clean code"],"title":"Hướng dẫn Style Javascript Airbnb (Phần 1)","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/airbnb-javascript-style-guide"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}